            Denise Piechnik
          
          
            
              Raised on a farm in mid-Michigan, I found my passion
              for science in California doing ecological research. Now
              residing in NY, I am an aspiring data scientist and a
              fiddle player.
              I recently left an academic position to change careers.
              I am seeking opportunities to apply my diverse skill set
              to sustainability and environmental problem-solving.
